Year Phase Milestone
1 0 Feasibility complete, PDR
2-3 1 Breadboard tests complete, TRR
4-6 2 EQ models qualified, CDR
7-8 3 Flight model built, TRR
9 4 Launch
10 4 Commissioning complete, ORR

